  "detailed_description": "A game where you can build amazing contraptions using the simple parts given to you.<br>such as:<br><br>computers using logic gates,<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2113210/extras/afa656a31754b8814e06ea40dfced3ab.avif?t=1663520722\" width=400 height=200 /></span><br><br>build buildings using the parts available to you, and add transportation systems for them!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2113210/extras/601123641f9029ff36c3d23b6fc8b966.avif?t=1663520722\" width=400 height=200 /></span><br><br>or create precise timing machines that execute the functions that you made them do.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2113210/extras/bda4a9113556b1dd9e099e796874bd6c.avif?t=1663520722\" width=400 height=200 /></span><br><br>features:<br>- simple building blocks that you can rely on to support your buildings.<br>- electrical cables to power components on and off.<br>- basic logic gates to create computers, calculators, etc...<br>- pistons, accelerators, and more blocks to move stuff around more efficiently.",
